    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052480/extras/1acca456ad4358cad9604b20c60ddf04.avif?t=1755051715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052480/extras_big/1acca456ad4358cad9604b20c60ddf04.avif?t=1755051715 width=800 height=282 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052480/extras/0b725340057e0aa4f0d2e84c819ab26b.avif?t=1755051715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052480/extras_big/0b725340057e0aa4f0d2e84c819ab26b.avif?t=1755051715 width=800 height=282 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052480/extras/ff29ad428313b664dc7167197f4bf328.avif?t=1755051715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052480/extras_big/ff29ad428313b664dc7167197f4bf328.avif?t=1755051715 width=800 height=282 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052480/extras/0a49070e7acb4a390b6ff80b8b174c0a.avif?t=1755051715\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052480/extras_big/0a49070e7acb4a390b6ff80b8b174c0a.avif?t=1755051715 width=800 height=282 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-<strong>继承王位</strong>-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有人可以拒绝权力的诱惑</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款游戏中，你将扮演一位王国的继承者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带领王国走向伟大！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-<strong>面对困境</strong>-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >王权的延续并非一帆风顺</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无数的困难正在接踵而至</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要精打细算平衡王国的方方面面</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >国库、军队、人民、资源、外交</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-<strong>做出选择-</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的每一个抉择都会影响王国的未来</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是爱民如子的明君，还是为了达成目的不择手段？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论你愿意与否，都需要做出改变</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-<strong>多个结局</strong>-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个王国都有属于它自己的故事</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是沦陷，还是伟大？亦或是销声匿迹？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一切都由你来决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>如果您对该游戏感兴趣，不妨点击添加愿望单！方便第一时间接收游戏发布、折扣、以及最新消息！</strong></p>",
